Michael Alon DAVIS, Applicant-Appellant,
v.
STATE of Iowa, Respondent-Appellee. No. 18-0844 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Michael Davis appeals the dismissal of his fourth postconviction-relief application. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
